tweets.text:
We must remember and reaffirm that gun violence is not an intractable problem. 

We will not accept it. We know what to do to solve it. 

@MomsDemand, @Everytown, @AMarch4OurLives, and so many others are making progress every day.

@realDonaldTrump You’ve set the precedent.

Your emergency declaration will be shutdown in the courts, as you admitted during your own presser that you didn’t need to do it.

The next president won’t be as dumb as you, though.
